{"id": 3059, "genre": 1000, "title": "日常中你都习惯了哪些避无可避的“微分神”状态？", "description": "“并没有完全走神，但好像也谈不上注意力集中”，这就是我一天大部分时刻的状态。（题图来自：iStock ©️ jesadaphorn）", "record_count": 8988, "comment_count": 16, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201911132122516JK12byxVNoTmrHZ.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-11-13T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 6036, "title": "日常中你都习惯了哪些避无可避的“微分神”状态？", "content": "你都习惯了哪些避无可避的“微分神”状态？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 349401, "content": "有任务必须马上记下来，否则很快会被海量信息冲掉", "image": "img/option/option/20191113200408YVp1dXt4U2mNvKlZ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349403, "content": "经常处于“记得有件事没做，但不记得是啥事”的状态", "image": "img/option/option/20191113202413ZbMyNdY7EvOlPJ4c.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349407, "content": "刚想做点正事，肌肉记忆还是会让自己点开社交媒体", "image": "img/option/option/20191113205304QC2fWMBKjHzlka81.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349410, "content": "习惯用音乐/电视剧/白噪音当 BGM，否则反而没法集中", "image": "img/option/option/201911132123504eu2B6aFORDoGqTN.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349400, "content": "一旦感觉无聊/焦虑，就会无意识地在手机上划来划去", "image": "img/option/option/20191113195945TXHLoNCavbr4AnOc.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349402, "content": "日常在十几个 app 之间切换，但每个都不会停很久", "image": "img/option/option/20191113201524m1p7tC6YazRI0odx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349404, "content": "开会/看书/工作十分钟，就会开始用手机/意念摸鱼", "image": "img/option/option/20191113203553mMd7UQ81BeFCqhaG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349412, "content": "另一方面，休息时又会忍不住走神去想工作的事", "image": "img/option/option/2019111321133614aFipLXR5TgEZlV.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 349413, "content": "我还好，完美避开了以上全部", "image": "img/option/option/20191113211233UDed6QwmcPV2HijK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}